### Exam API Endpoints

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api/Exam

### Schedule New Exam
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "examName": "First Terminal Examination 2026",
  "examType": "terminal",
  "class": "10",
  "academicYear": "2025-2026",
  "startDate": "2026-03-15",
  "endDate": "2026-03-20",
  "venue": "Main Examination Hall",
  "instructions": "Students must bring their admit cards and arrive 30 minutes before the exam time.",
  "examSubjects": [
    {
      "subject": "mathematics",
      "date": "2026-03-15",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    },
    {
      "subject": "science",
      "date": "2026-03-16",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    },
    {
      "subject": "english",
      "date": "2026-03-17",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    }
  ]
}

### Get All Exams
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Exams with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&classFilter=10&academicYear=2025-2026
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Exam By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update Exam
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "examName": "First Terminal Examination 2026 - Updated",
  "examType": "terminal",
  "class": "10",
  "academicYear": "2025-2026",
  "startDate": "2026-03-15",
  "endDate": "2026-03-20",
  "venue": "Main Examination Hall - Room A",
  "instructions": "Updated instructions: Students must bring their admit cards and arrive 30 minutes before the exam time. No electronic devices allowed.",
  "examSubjects": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "subject": "mathematics",
      "date": "2026-03-15",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "subject": "science",
      "date": "2026-03-16",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "subject": "english",
      "date": "2026-03-17",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    },
    {
      "subject": "hindi",
      "date": "2026-03-18",
      "startTime": "09:00:00",
      "endTime": "12:00:00",
      "maxMarks": 100
    }
  ]
}

### Delete Exam
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE